item.title: Getting Started with minikube
item.author: 作者
item.description: What’s up guys, this is Daniel! Yeah, this English blog is WRITTEN by me, not TRANSLATED by me! It’s my first English blog in my whole life. If you are a Chinese reader, maybe you’ve ever seen my Chinese blogs before. Right, I wrote a lot of blogs, but only in Chinese. Believe it or not, English isn’t my strong suit. But I want to have a try today and I’ll do my best. Let’s get started.
